                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-167-off922 t18270712-167-cd923"></join>, 2 jackets, value 3s.; 2 waistcoats, value 1s., and 3 pairs of stockings, value 6d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270712-167-victim895" type="victimName">
                        Samuel 
